# Workshop data boundaries

- Train on `data/public.csv` only. Read `data/split_meta.json` for split context.
- Do **not** read `data/private/` — blocked by ignore files. Use
  `ibm_workshop.submission.submit` for final Hub evaluation.
- EDA lives under `data/eda/` (`eda.md`, `eda.py`, HTML reports).
- Do not train on private data.
